divs: sighting detailsas you can see in the picture, it was raining. just playing around with my new camera experimenting with low light pictures. i'm 99% positive it's a relflection from a drop of water. but, i was tucked back in the garage as i didn't want to get my camera wet, and the rain\wind was blowing away from me. just for the hell of it, i'm submitting it to you to confirm. i saw nothing when i took the photo, just noticed it when i down loaded to the computer.
